Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory180.png'}
{2: 'King', 3: '—I will be back!', 4: '1'}
{3: "Unlike his formidable strength, the King's last words were very unimpressive."}
{3: 'The King resentfully disappeared in the wind, leaving nothing behind.'}
{2: 'Did we win?', 3: '10', 4: 'Is anyone hurt?', 5: '12'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Yeah, the victory is ours.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Hehe, of course not. Thanks to your strategy, Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Have we resolved the crisis of this world?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Goddess', 3: "No, there's one last step.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'The Goddess suddenly walked out from the crowd. She stopped at where the King was standing.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'What do you mean?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Goddess', 3: 'The Goddess has given the body back to me temporarily. So, right now, standing in front of you...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Demon King', 3: 'This blond version of me... Is the Demon King!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Are you the same as the King...?', 3: '27', 4: "I'm sorry, I don't understand?", 5: '28'}
{2: 'Demon King', 3: 'I have no plan to control any system. But as the Demon King, I must have a battle against the heroes!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Demon King', 3: 'What I mean is... Now is the classic ending!', 4: '1'}
{3: "Under the Demon King's control, the castle suddenly transformed. She ascended into the sky while the ground that everyone was standing on kept falling down."}
{2: 'Demon King', 3: 'Heroes, I will unleash all the Demons to take our final revenge against the humans. Now, come and stop me.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Demon King', 3: 'Defeat me to put an end on this game, and complete what the previous heroes failed to do!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'System', 3: 'Main quest updated: Defeat the Demon King to save the world.'}
